OL,7,FLearner drivers are having to wait for
OL,8,Fup to six months in parts of the UK to
OL,9,Fsit their test due to a Covid backlog,
OL,10,Fwith delays set to worsen due to
OL,11,Fongoing strikes and winter weather.
OL,13,FThe average wait time in the UK for a
OL,14,Ftest is around 15.7 weeks, or around
OL,15,Ffour months, compared to just six weeks
OL,16,Fpre-pandemic, the Driver and Vehicle
OL,17,FStandards Agency (DVSA) said.
OL,3,CDriving test waits reach 6 months in
OL,4,Csome parts of UK amid strikes, cold
OL,5,Csnap and Covid backlog
